translations.content:
The hotel is very new, well decorated and clean;
The laundry room has a dryer, a Panasonic one;
Good front desk service, Sprite/Coke, plus oranges for free, great hotel

comments.translatedContent:
Very close to the subway station
The service attitude is super good, there are oranges at the front desk, and the takeaway orders will be delivered by robots;
The breakfast is very rich, including bread, milk, orange juice, steamed buns, steamed dumplings, steamed noodles, fried rice, and various porridges;
The room is fully equipped with automatic curtains, hand sanitizer, and shampoo, all of which are orange-flavored. I like them very much.
